---
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <title>Heritage Coastal | Respectful Property Transitions</title>
    <meta
      name="description"
      content="Heritage Coastal works with homeowners, families, and estates seeking a private, respectful, and thoughtful transition of coastal properties."
    />
    <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />

    <style is:inline>
      :root {
        --navy: #162233;
        --navy-soft: #223247;
        --green: #24372d;
        --green-soft: #33483c;
        --cream: #f4efe4;
        --paper: #fbf8f1;
        --linen: #ebe2d2;
        --gold: #b79b5b;
        --gold-soft: #d8c794;
        --ink: #1d2a24;
        --muted: #6e746c;
        --line: rgba(36, 55, 45, 0.18);
        --shadow: 0 26px 80px rgba(22, 34, 51, 0.16);
      }

      * {
        box-sizing: border-box;
      }

      html {
        scroll-behavior: smooth;
      }

      body {
        margin: 0;
        background: var(--paper);
        color: var(--ink);
        font-family: Georgia, "Times New Roman", serif;
      }

      a {
        color: inherit;
      }

      .hero {
        min-height: 100vh;
        color: white;
        background:
          linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(22, 34, 51, 0.92), rgba(22, 34, 51, 0.72) 48%, rgba(22, 34, 51, 0.35)),
          url("hhttps://images.unsplash.com/photo-1507525428034-b723cf961d3e?auto=format&fit=crop&w=2400&q=85");
        background-size: cover;
        background-position: center;
      }

      .nav {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
        align-items: center;
        padding: 30px clamp(24px, 6vw, 86px);
      }

      .brand-mark {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 14px;
        letter-spacing: 0.24em;
        font-size: 13px;
        font-weight: 700;
      }

      .monogram {
        display: grid;
        place-items: center;
        width: 38px;
        height: 38px;
        border: 1px solid rgba(216, 199, 148, 0.8);
        color: var(--gold-soft);
        letter-spacing: 0;
        font-size: 20px;
      }

      .nav-note {
        color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.76);
        font-size: 15px;
        letter-spacing: 0.04em;
      }

      .hero-inner {
        max-width: 1030px;
        padding: 116px clamp(24px, 6vw, 86px) 128px;
      }

      .eyebrow {
        color: var(--gold-soft);
        letter-spacing: 0.22em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        font-size: 13px;
        margin-bottom: 26px;
      }

      h1,
      h2,
      h3,
      p {
        margin-top: 0;
      }

      h1 {
        max-width: 950px;
        font-size: clamp(48px, 7vw, 92px);
        line-height: 0.96;
        letter-spacing: -0.045em;
        font-weight: 400;
        margin-bottom: 34px;
      }

      .hero-copy {
        max-width: 690px;
        font-size: clamp(19px, 2vw, 23px);
        line-height: 1.68;
        color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.88);
        margin-bottom: 42px;
      }

      .actions {
        display: flex;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        gap: 16px;
      }

      .button {
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        min-height: 52px;
        padding: 15px 26px;
        text-decoration: none;
        border-radius: 0;
        font-size: 15px;
        letter-spacing: 0.04em;
        transition: transform 180ms ease, background 180ms ease, border-color 180ms ease;
      }

      .button:hover {
        transform: translateY(-1px);
      }

      .button-primary {
        background: var(--gold-soft);
        color: var(--navy);
      }

      .button-secondary {
        border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.48);
        color: white;
      }

      .panel {
        width: min(1120px, calc(100% - 48px));
        margin: -72px auto 0;
        background: var(--paper);
        box-shadow: var(--shadow);
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
        border: 1px solid rgba(183, 155, 91, 0.26);
        position: relative;
        z-index: 2;
      }

      .panel-item {
        padding: 34px;
        border-right: 1px solid var(--line);
      }

      .panel-item:last-child {
        border-right: 0;
      }

      .panel-item strong {
        display: block;
        color: var(--navy);
        font-size: 22px;
        font-weight: 400;
        margin-bottom: 10px;
      }

      .panel-item span {
        color: var(--muted);
        font-size: 16px;
        line-height: 1.55;
      }

      section {
        padding: 104px clamp(24px, 6vw, 86px);
      }

      .split {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 0.9fr 1.1fr;
        gap: clamp(48px, 8vw, 110px);
        align-items: start;
      }

      .label {
        color: var(--gold);
        letter-spacing: 0.2em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        font-size: 12px;
        font-weight: 700;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
      }

      h2 {
        color: var(--navy);
        font-size: clamp(34px, 4.5vw, 60px);
        line-height: 1.08;
        letter-spacing: -0.035em;
        font-weight: 400;
      }

      .text p {
        color: var(--muted);
        font-size: 20px;
        line-height: 1.78;
        margin-bottom: 24px;
      }

      .cream {
        background: var(--cream);
      }

      .principles-head {
        max-width: 760px;
      }

      .cards {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
        gap: 24px;
        margin-top: 54px;
      }

      .card {
        background: var(--paper);
        border: 1px solid var(--line);
        padding: 40px 36px;
        min-height: 292px;
      }

      .num {
        color: var(--gold);
        letter-spacing: 0.16em;
        font-size: 13px;
        font-weight: 700;
        margin-bottom: 30px;
      }

      h3 {
        color: var(--navy);
        font-size: 28px;
        line-height: 1.18;
        font-weight: 400;
        margin-bottom: 18px;
      }

      .card p {
        color: var(--muted);
        font-size: 18px;
        line-height: 1.7;
      }

      .process-list {
        margin-top: 46px;
        border-top: 1px solid var(--line);
      }

      .step {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 150px 1fr;
        gap: 34px;
        padding: 34px 0;
        border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
      }

      .step strong {
        color: var(--gold);
        letter-spacing: 0.16em;
        font-size: 13px;
      }

      .step p {
        color: var(--muted);
        font-size: 20px;
        line-height: 1.7;
        margin: 0;
      }

      .statement {
        background: var(--navy);
        color: white;
        text-align: center;
        padding: 110px clamp(24px, 9vw, 130px);
      }

      .statement p {
        max-width: 1120px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        font-size: clamp(30px, 4.4vw, 58px);
        line-height: 1.22;
        letter-spacing: -0.035em;
        font-weight: 400;
      }

      .contact-card {
        background: var(--cream);
        border: 1px solid var(--line);
        padding: 46px;
      }

      .contact-card p {
        color: var(--muted);
        font-size: 20px;
        line-height: 1.72;
      }

      .email-link {
        color: var(--navy);
        text-decoration: none;
        border-bottom: 1px solid var(--gold);
      }

      footer {
        background: var(--navy);
        color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.68);
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
        gap: 22px;
        padding: 32px clamp(24px, 6vw, 86px);
        font-size: 14px;
      }

      @media (max-width: 900px) {
        .nav {
          align-items: flex-start;
          gap: 18px;
          flex-direction: column;
        }

        .hero-inner {
          padding-top: 76px;
        }

        .panel,
        .split,
        .cards,
        .step {
          grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        }

        .panel-item {
          border-right: 0;
          border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
        }

        .panel-item:last-child {
          border-bottom: 0;
        }

        section {
          padding-top: 76px;
          padding-bottom: 76px;
        }

        footer {
          flex-direction: column;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>

  <body>
    <main>
      <section class="hero">
        <nav class="nav" aria-label="Main navigation">
          <div class="brand-mark">
            <span class="monogram">H</span>
            <span>HERITAGE COASTAL</span>
          </div>
          <div class="nav-note">Private property transitions</div>
        </nav>

        <div class="hero-inner">
          <div class="eyebrow">Stewardship · Continuity · Respect</div>
          <h1>For owners considering the next chapter of a cherished property.</h1>
          <p class="hero-copy">
            Heritage Coastal works directly with homeowners, families, and estates seeking a private, thoughtful, and dignified transition of coastal real estate.
          </p>
          <div class="actions">
            <a class="button button-primary" href="mailto:info@heritagecoastal.com">Start a Private Conversation</a>
            <a class="button button-secondary" href="#approach">Our Approach</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <div class="panel" aria-label="Heritage Coastal commitments">
        <div class="panel-item">
          <strong>Private</strong>
          <span>Quiet conversations without public listings, showings, or neighborhood speculation.</span>
        </div>
        <div class="panel-item">
          <strong>Patient</strong>
          <span>Flexible timing for families, estates, and owners who need room to decide carefully.</span>
        </div>
        <div class="panel-item">
          <strong>Direct</strong>
          <span>Clear proposals, straightforward terms, and no unnecessary process.</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <section class="split" id="approach">
        <div>
          <div class="label">Our Belief</div>
          <h2>A home is not merely an asset. It is a record of care.</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="text">
          <p>
            Many properties carry decades of family history, neighborhood memory, and personal investment. We approach those conversations with patience, discretion, and respect.
          </p>
          <p>
            Our role is simple: to provide a clear path for owners who may be ready to sell, but do not want pressure, spectacle, or a rushed public process.
          </p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="cream">
        <div class="principles-head">
          <div class="label">Principles</div>
          <h2>Quiet, direct, and considerate.</h2>
        </div>

        <div class="cards">
          <article class="card">
            <div class="num">01</div>
            <h3>Respect for the owner</h3>
            <p>We move at a pace that suits the family, not the market. No hard sell. No manufactured urgency. No public pressure.</p>
          </article>

          <article class="card">
            <div class="num">02</div>
            <h3>Respect for the property</h3>
            <p>Every property has a story. We take time to understand its history, condition, setting, and the owner’s hopes for what comes next.</p>
          </article>

          <article class="card">
            <div class="num">03</div>
            <h3>Respect for privacy</h3>
            <p>Conversations remain private. We can discuss options quietly, without listing, staging, repeated showings, or speculation.</p>
          </article>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section>
        <div class="split">
          <div>
            <div class="label">How It Works</div>
            <h2>A simpler alternative to a public sale.</h2>
          </div>
          <div>
            <div class="process-list">
              <div class="step">
                <strong>FIRST</strong>
                <p>We have a private conversation to understand the property, the timing, and whether a direct transaction may be appropriate.</p>
              </div>
              <div class="step">
                <strong>SECOND</strong>
                <p>If there is mutual interest, we review the property carefully and provide a clear proposal without requiring repairs, staging, or open houses.</p>
              </div>
              <div class="step">
                <strong>THIRD</strong>
                <p>The owner chooses the path and timing. We can accommodate flexible closing dates, estate situations, family transitions, and as-is sales.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="statement">
        <p>We believe the best transactions are not extracted. They are earned through patience, clarity, and trust.</p>
      </section>

      <section class="split">
        <div>
          <div class="label">Contact</div>
          <h2>Begin with a private note.</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="contact-card">
          <p>
            If you are considering a sale, managing an estate, or simply weighing options for a coastal property, we welcome a confidential conversation.
          </p>
          <p>Email: <a class="email-link" href="mailto:info@heritagecoastal.com">info@heritagecoastal.com</a></p>
        </div>
      </section>
    </main>

    <footer>
      <div>© 2026 Heritage Coastal</div>
      <div>Private acquisitions of coastal homes and legacy properties</div>
    </footer>
  </body>
</html>
